{"tid":2002404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"條街愈黎愈多燈柱，話因為要捉下扔垃圾","createTime":"2020-05-05T07:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T10:08:47.000Z","uid":205339,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ba621d54d7c94f0bd49fac60df0a50134bcc8604","tid":2002404,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T07:16:54.000Z","msg":"香港政府為左阻止人亂拋垃圾，所以政府就借機起大大枝CCTV係度影，你唔會天真到以為個鏡頭只會影到人亂拋垃圾掛？<br />\n<br />\n而今日幾個要捉所謂飛車的「區議員」目的就係要香港人認同捉飛車，然後馬路上就會忽然多左好多白鴿籠。你以為白鴿籠只係捉快車？跟黃絲「校車」跟到入屋都可以呀。<br />\n<br />\n政府已經借拋垃圾及瘟疫去安裝CCTV，仲要有人面識別功能。呢群區議員就係做緊呢D野去比政府落手裝CCTV，如果咁樣都睇唔到，早撚D死啦黃絲。<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀，快D去捉人紅燈過馬路，捉人裝曬衫竹，幫手黨鐵捉人係月台內進食，唔捉唔影大頭正契弟。<br />\n<br />\n香港人死清光，再冇人犯法，更加冇噪音。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o24TwmT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo24TwmT.jpg&h=5f4f7190&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a532950bb7fb20f15774526d31d1dc5b686d3b1f","tid":2002404,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1219657624789220/posts/2930456620375970/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1219657624789220%2Fposts%2F2930456620375970%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=304c3739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1219657624789220/posts/2930456620375970/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"e8e45f42aa62a71fdd3eba10bef39b58c9d0d68b","tid":2002404,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"強烈支持熱普城進攻人大代表！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2002253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2002253</a>"},{"pid":"4b064534198dc4d87eac06b6d7d5811d8bcaa803","tid":2002404,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔知點解篇文睇落好大陣膠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c79b1456f8dbdfd495d4b584